quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  45,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  45,1,Haa-Meeem
  45,2,is kitaab ka utaara jana khuday-e ghalib ( aur ) Dana ( ki taraf ) se hai
  45,3,be shak asmano aur zameen mein imaan walon ke liye ( khuda ki qudrat ki ) nishanain hain
  45,4,aur tumhari paidaiesh mein bhi. aur janwaron mein bhi jin ko woh phelata hai yaqeen karne walon ke liye nishanain hain
  45,5,aur raat aur din ke agay peechay anay jaane mein aur woh jo khuda ne aasman sezarya rizaq nazil farmaya phir is se zameen ko is ke mrjane ke baad zindahkiya is mein aur hawaon ke badalny mein aqal walon ke liye nishanain hain
  45,6,yeh khuda ki ayatain hain jo hum tum ko sachaai ke sath parh kar sunaate hain. to yeh khuda aur is ki aayton ke baad kis baat par imaan layein ge ?
  45,7,har jhutay gunehgaar par afsos hai
  45,8,( ke ) khuda ki ayatain is ko parh kar sunai jati hain to un ko sun to laita hai ( magar ) phir ghuroor se zid karta hai ke goya un ko suna hi nahi. so aisay shakhs ko dukh dainay walay azaab ki khushkhabri suna do
  45,9,aur jab hamari kuch ayatain usay maloom hoti hain to un ki hansi urata hai. aisay logon ke liye zaleel karne wala azaab hai
  45,10,un ke samnay dozakh hai. aur jo kaam woh karte rahay kuch bhi un ke kaam nah ayen ge. aur nah wohi ( kaam ayen ge ) jin ko unhon ne khuda ke siwa mabood bana rakha tha. aur un ke liye bara azaab hai
  45,11,yeh hadaayat ( ki kitaab ) hai. aur jo log apne perwar-digaar ki aayton se inkaar karte hain un ko sakht qisam ka dard dainay wala azaab hoga
  45,12,khuda hi to hai jis ne darya ko tumahray qaboo kardiya taakay is ke hukum se is mein kashtiyan chalein aur taakay tum is ke fazl se ( muaash ) talaash karo aur taakay shukar karo
  45,13,aur jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab ko apne ( hukum ) se tumahray kaam mein laga diya. jo log ghhor karte hain un ke liye is mein ( qudrat khuda ki ) nishanain hain
  45,14,mominoun se keh do ke jo log khuda ke dinon ki ( jo aamaal ke badlay ke liye muqarrar hain ) tawaqqa nahi rakhtay un se dar guzar karen. taakay woh un logon ko un ke aamaal ka badlay day
  45,15,jo koi amal naik kere ga to apne liye. aur jo buray kaam kere ga to un ka zarrar isi ko hoga. phir tum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout kar jao ge
  45,16,aur hum ne bani Israel ko kitaab ( hadaayat ) aur hukoomat aur nabuwat bakhsh aur pakeeza cheeze ataa farmaen aur ahal aalam par fazeelat di
  45,17,aur un ko deen ke baray mein daleelen ataa kee. to unhon ne jo ikhtilaafkiya to ilm aa chuknay ke baad aapas ki zid sekiya. be shak tumhara perwar-digaar qayamat ke din un mein un baton ka jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte they faisla kere ga
  45,18,phir hum ne tum ko deen ke khulay raste par ( qaim ) kar diya to isi ( raste ) par chalay chalo aur نادانوں ki khawahishon ke peechay nah chalna
  45,19,yeh khuda ke samnay tumahray kisi kaam nahi ayen ge. aur zalim log aik dosray ke dost hotay hain. aur khuda parhaiz garon ka dost hai
  45,20,yeh quran logon ke liye danai ki baatein hain aur jo yaqeen rakhtay hain un ke liye hadaayat aur rehmat hai
  45,21,jo log buray kaam karte hainkiya woh yeh khayaal karte hain ke hum un ko un logon jaissa kar dein ge jo imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay aur un ki zindagi aur mout yaksaa hogi. yeh jo daaway karte hain buray hain
  45,22,aur khuda ne asmano aur zameen ko hikmat se pedakiya hai aur taakay har shakhs apne aamaal ka badla paye aur un par zulm nahikiya jaye ga
  45,23,bhala tum ne is shakhs ko dekha jis ne apni khwahish ko mabood bana rakha hai aur bawajood jan-nay bojhne ke ( gumraah ho raha hai to ) khuda ne ( bhi ) is ko gumraah kardiya aur is ke kaanon aur dil par mohar laga di aur is ki aankhon par parda daal diya. ab khuda ke siwa is ko kon raah par la sakta hai. bhala tum kyun nasiyaat nahi pakarte ?
  45,24,aur kehte hain ke hamari zindagi to sirf duniya hi ki hai ke ( yahin ) martay aur jeetay hain aur hamein to zamana maar deta hai. aur un ko is ka kuch ilm nahi. sirf zan se kaam letay hain
  45,25,aur jab un ke samnay hamari khuli khuli ayatain parhi jati hain to un ki yahi Hujjat hoti hai ke agar tum sachey ho to hamaray baap dada ko ( zindah kar ) lao
  45,26,keh do ke khuda hi tum ko jaan bkhshta hai phir ( wohi ) tum ko mout deta hai phir tum ko qayamat ke roz jis ( ke anay ) mein kuch shak nahi tum ko jama kere ga lekin bohat se log nahi jantay
  45,27,aur asmano aur zameen ki badshahat khuda hi ki hai. aur jis roz qayamat barpaa hogi is roz ahal baatil khasaray mein par jayen ge
  45,28,aur tum har aik firqay ko dekho ge ke ghutnon ke bil betha hoga. aur har aik jamaat apni kitaab ( aamaal ) ki taraf baalaaee jaye gi. jo kuch tum karte rahay ho aaj tum ko is ka badla diya jaye ga
  45,29,yeh hamari kitaab tumahray baray mein sach sach bayan kardey gi. jo kuch tumkiya karte they hum lkhwate jatay hain
  45,30,to jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un ka perwar-digaar inhen rehmat ( ke baagh ) mein daakhil kere ga. yahi Sarih kamyabi hai
  45,31,aur jinhon ne kufarkiya. ( un se kaha jaye ga ke ) bhala hamari ayatain tum ko parh kar sunai nahi jati theen? phir tum ne taqqaburkiya aur tum nafarman log they
  45,32,aur jab kaha jata tha ke khuda ka wada sacha hai aur qayamat mein kuch shak nahi to tum kehte they hum nahi jantay ke qayamatkiya hai. hum is ko mehez Zanni khayaal karte hain aur hamein yaqeen nahi aata
  45,33,aur un ke aamaal ki buraiyan un par zahir ho jaien gi aur jis ( azaab ) ki woh hansi uratye they woh un ko aaghire ga
  45,34,aur kaha jaye ga ke jis terhan tum ne is din ke anay ko bhala rakha tha. isi terhan aaj hum tumhe bhala den ge aur tumhara thikana dozakh hai aur koi tumhara madadgaar nahi
  45,35,yeh is liye ke tum ne khuda ki aayton ko mkhol bana rakha tha aur duniya ki zindagi ne tum ko dhokay mein daal rakha tha. so aaj yeh log nah dozakh se nikalay jayen ge aur nah un ki tauba qubool ki jaye gi
  45,36,pas khuda hi ko har terhan ki tareef ( sazawar ) hai jo asmano ka maalik aur zameen ka maalik aur tamam Jahan ka perwar-digaar hai
  45,37,aur asmano aur zameen mein usi ke liye barayi hai. aur woh ghalib aur Dana hai
